dcterms:creator: S. Koelstra
et al.
dcterms:description: A comprehensive dataset that includes EEG signals of music listening, collected from 32 subjects who watched forty 1-min long music videos while having their EEG recorded. Subjects rated the emotions elicited in 5 dimensions: valence, arousal, dominance, liking, and familiarity.
dcterms:title: DEAP Dataset
